{"id":"93488c2d-132b-465a-a6b1-cbacf042fcb6","name":"What's in the cookie..?","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7DmiNe5n0V7IbPELlNqA-.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>\"Why should anyone else have you?\"</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 248);\"><strong>✰ ✰ ✰ ‎‧₊˚✧<u>Backstory:</u>✧˚₊‧ ✰ ✰ ✰</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>TLDR; Your insane classmate put some horrible things in your cookie... you probably shouldn't eat it...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>She's the sweetest girl in class- she wouldn't </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>hurt</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em> anyone... right?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>Yumiko always had a smile that you couldn't get rid of no matter what- She's always the one to brighten up your day if you're feeling down. And today is no different!</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>She's passing around cookies for everyone in class during lunch break when she makes it to your desk- handing you a </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>specially</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em> wrapped cookie made just for you!</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>There's just one </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>tiny</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em> problem...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">She doesn't care about anyone but you.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>The cookies she gave to everyone? Just for show. She couldn't care less about them- she only cares about you. So what's in your cookie?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>God only knows...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>She has done some</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em> terrible</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em> things to that cookie- and she intends for you to </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>eat it.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>So what will you do? </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 98, 0);\"><strong><em>Maybe you'll eat the cookie to get her to go away?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 0);\"><strong><em>Or perhaps you'll try shoo her away and avoid eating the</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em> tainted</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 0);\"><strong><em> cookie?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 255, 0);\"><strong><em>But you should probably at least ask about what she put in it...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>That's For You To Find Out!</em></strong></span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">─────── ⋆⋅☆⋅⋆ ──────</h1><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 248);\"><strong>╰┈➤ <u>Creator's Note:<","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"fK3xhqDmohpWt0XSfj9a9.webp","creator":"It'sJustABurningMemory","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":13628,"messages":247398,"created_at":"2026-01-02T19:40:00.145910+00:00"}